show.description: Ek nayi nurse, ek strict officer, aur ek love story jo battlefield ke rules todti hai! The Officer Fell for Me mein hai passion, politics aur ek aisi kahani jo duty aur desire ke beech jujhti hai. Kya Carson aur Gordon ek dusre ko protect karte karte dil haar baithenge?
